WEBVTT

00:01.880 --> 00:02.960
Palm and back of hand

00:04.000 --> 00:05.040
I love both

00:10.320 --> 00:11.440
Before, the elder son

00:11.680 --> 00:13.480
Came to help me make elixirs

00:14.280 --> 00:15.640
Now he doesn't come anymore

00:16.040 --> 00:17.960
Your mother wants to see her son but can't

00:18.680 --> 00:19.920
Can only be cross with me every day

00:20.320 --> 00:21.440
Nothing is right

00:21.520 --> 00:22.560
Everything is wrong

00:25.920 --> 00:26.920
Blame this old servant for speaking too much

00:27.160 --> 00:28.200
Had to mention Prince of Ning

00:28.640 --> 00:29.720
Making Your Majesty sad

00:31.000 --> 00:31.640
However

00:32.200 --> 00:34.000
Prince of Ning has been confined for so long

00:34.400 --> 00:35.240
Surely in his heart

00:35.240 --> 00:36.800
He misses Your Majesty and the Empress

00:37.640 --> 00:38.320
Perhaps

00:39.240 --> 00:40.280
Let Prince of Ning out

00:40.560 --> 00:41.520
To help Your Majesty make elixirs

00:44.760 --> 00:46.800
This elder son is disappointing

00:47.520 --> 00:48.800
I had him build a canal

00:49.400 --> 00:51.720
He caused the people of Qing Province to rebel

00:54.080 --> 00:56.160
If I just release him

00:58.160 --> 00:59.000
Second son, tell me

00:59.560 --> 01:00.640
What should I do

01:00.640 --> 01:03.520
To give the world an answer?
